    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 20</em>, <em>Ultimate Combat pg. 130</em></p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\">Statistics</h3><p><strong>Cost</strong> 3 gp <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><strong>Damage</strong> 1d2 (small), 1d3 (medium); <strong>Critical</strong> 19-20/x2; <strong>Range</strong> -; <strong>Type</strong> P; <strong>Special</strong> see text</p><p><strong>Category</strong> Light; <strong>Proficiency</strong> Exotic</p><p><strong>Weapon Groups</strong> Close; Monk</p><h3 class=\"framing\">Description</h3><p>This weapon is used to augment unarmed martial techniques. It consists of an 8- to 10-inch-long, dual-pointed steel spike set on swivels and mounted on a ring, so that it can be spun around at high speeds when slipped over the wielder's ring finger. The ring prevents the wielder from being disarmed and turns unarmed strikes into piercing attacks.</p>",
